Package de.szut.dqi12.cheftrainer.server.databasecommunication

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommunityManagement
    This class is used to communicate with the database.
    DatabaseUtils
    This class provides a few simple method, to communicate with the database or to check ResultSets.
    LogicManagement
    This class provides functions to map a Player to a Manager and some other simple functions, which are mostly used by the TeamGenerator.
    PlayerManagement
    This class is used to Initialize the Database, when the server starts the first time.
    PointManagement
    This cless is used to send Query to the database to update the points of players.
    SchedulePointManagement
    This class is used to write points of players to the databse.
    ServerPropertiesManagement
    This class is used to read/write server specific properties to the database.
    TransfermarketManagement
    The TransfermarketManagement is used to send queries according or the transfermarket, the transactions and offers to the database and workup the results.
    UserManagement
    This class handles the User registration and login.
